# Whitelist repo: ships ONLY the Deathwatch mod source + its one build-tooling customization.
# Everything else (the Owlcat template, Unity Library, builds) is intentionally untracked;
# see README.md "Building from source".
/*
!/.gitignore
!/README.md
!/DESIGN_NOTES.md
!/Assets
/Assets/*
!/Assets/Modifications
/Assets/Modifications/*
!/Assets/Modifications/DeathwatchMod
!/Assets/Modifications/DeathwatchMod.meta
!/Assets/Editor
/Assets/Editor/*
!/Assets/Editor/Build
/Assets/Editor/Build/*
!/Assets/Editor/Build/Tasks
/Assets/Editor/Build/Tasks/*
!/Assets/Editor/Build/Tasks/PrepareArtifacts.cs
!/Assets/Editor/Build/Tasks/PrepareArtifacts.cs.meta

# Auto-generated at build time (PrepareBuild wipes and regenerates it)
/Assets/Modifications/DeathwatchMod/Generated/
Generated.meta
